		"body": "Fixes #8578\r\n\r\nWhen a note has a source_url (e.g. clipped from the web), a clickable link now shows up in the editor's status bar. Clicking it opens the original page in the browser.\r\n\r\nChanges:\r\n- StatusBar.tsx: added sourceUrl prop, renders a link with truncation for long URLs\r\n- NoteEditor.tsx: passes formNote.source_url to the StatusBar\r\n",
